thread.title: Regional volleyball pairings released

title: Regional volleyball pairings released
text:
The Gazette October 1, 2015 | 5:19 pm 
The Iowa Girls High School Athletic Union released postseason volleyball pairings for all five classes Thursday. 
Play begins in Class 1A, 2A and 3A Oct. 20, and Class 4A and 5A Oct. 21. 
Regional winners advance to the state tournament, which takes place Nov. 10-13 at the U.S. Cellular Center in Cedar Rapids.
